# Modular Dashboard (FastAPI + React) â€” Crypto Widgets

This project implements a small modular dashboard with 4 widgets:

- Top Coins (supports "load more" lazy loading)
- Price Movements (top gainers & losers)  
- Alerts (coins with 24h change above threshold)
- Market Cap (global market cap & active coins)

Backend: FastAPI (Light DDD modules)

## Quickstart

### Using Docker (Recommended)

```bash
# Build and start services
docker-compose up -d

# View logs
docker-compose logs -f

# Stop services
docker-compose down
```

The API will be available at <http://localhost:8000>

### Manual Setup

```bash
# Create and activate virtual environment
cd backend
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate    # Windows: .venv\Scripts\activate

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Start development server
uvicorn app.main:app --reload --port 8000
```

## API Documentation

Once running, visit:

- Swagger UI: <http://localhost:8000/docs>
- ReDoc: <http://localhost:8000/redoc>
